ort.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己人嘛，客客氣氣送佢離開，佢走緊嘅時候我地仲要大聲叫「同志們辛苦了！」，受到如此高規格禮遇，對方想必喜極而泣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n#永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進<br />\n#Follow 大波臭閪 = 曱甴<br />\n#Follow 立場姐姐 &amp; 攬炒巴 = 君子"},{"pid":"aac4d2fe21e943f0700aa391fe9d6a4ffa9a3824","tid":1481390,"uid":303181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:21:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a165b18b2ea02f052c9422c9efb35fd9f7a4dfbe","tid":1481390,"uid":306576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T20:33:25.000Z","msg":"樓豬5毛，blocked"}]}